{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Call for a Public Inquiry into pro-Iran Influence on UK Politics & Democracy",
        "additional_details": "We feel that the Iranian sponsorship of the aggressors of the October 7th 2023 war & the October 8th 2023 war began by Iranian-backed Lebanese militia and the later aggression from Yemeni militia against UK ally Israel, together with the UK\u2019s political response underline the urgent need to scrutinise how Iranian-sponsored organisations, networks & lobbying efforts may influence universities, government decisions & public debate.",
        "background": "We are concerned about reports of Iranian state\u2011linked and pro-Iran lobbying activity in UK politics. We believe it is important to determine the scope and impact of any such influence campaigns.",
